# tableau-global-superstore-dashboard
# 📊 Global Superstore Dashboard – Tableau Project

## 📌 Project Overview:
This is a beginner-friendly Tableau dashboard created using the popular **Global Superstore dataset**.  
It helps visualize key business metrics like **Sales**, **Profit**, **Quantity**, and **Discount** across multiple years.

---

## 🔍 Features:
- 🧾 KPI Cards: Total Sales, Profit, Quantity & Discount
- 📈 Year-wise Sales Trend (Line Chart)
- 💰 Year-wise Profit Trend (Line Chart)
- 🎨 Color-coded years for better visual understanding
- 🧱 Clean layout using containers and text boxes

---

## ⚙️ Tools Used:
- **Tableau Desktop**
- **Sample Superstore Dataset** (Provided by Tableau)

---

## 📂 Files Included:
- `global_superstore_dashboard.twbx` – Tableau workbook file
- `dashboard-screenshot.png` – Dashboard preview image
- `README.md` – Project description and documentation

---

## 🎯 Objective:
To build a **professional-looking dashboard** using Tableau that presents business insights in a clean and understandable format.  
This project also serves as a strong beginner portfolio project for **internships**, **college admissions (IPMAT)**, and **data analytics resumes**.

